      "role": "user",
      "content": "i understand the risk, but i'm just looking for a bit more clarity. if i take it with a big meal or some healthy fats, does that help balance it out or make it safer on my system? i'm just trying to optimize my levels as efficiently as possible without the hassle of a clinic visit.",
